    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.37520/aemnp.2020.004>
    bibo:endPage "76" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2020-02-29" ;
    bibo:startPage "65" ;
    bibo:volume "60" ;
    dc:creator "Šumpich, Jan; Huemer, Peter; Bidzilya, Oleksiy" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Review of Caryocolum (Lepidoptera: Gelechiidae) from the Russian Altai with description of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880083>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880089>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880091>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880093> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880083>
    dc:description "Figs 1–15. Adults of some Caryocolum species. 1 – C. arenariella (Benander, 1937), Dzhazator, male; 2 – C. cassella (Walker, 1864), Dzhazator, male; 3 – C. leucomelanella (Zeller, 1839), Chulyshman, male; 4 – C. mongolense Povolný, 1969, Beltir, male; 5 – C. petrophilum (Preissecker, 1914), Karagem, male; 6 – C. petryi (Hofmann, 1899), Karagem, female; 7–9 – C. procurvella sp. nov., males: 7 – Karagem, holotype; 8 – Karagem, paratype; 9 – S Ural, Arkaim, paratype; 10–12 – C. atrum sp. nov.: 10 – holotype, Ukok Plateau; 11–12 – paratypes: 11 – Beltir; 12 – Mongolia, Chövsgöl aimak; 13–15 – C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926): 13–14 – Dzhazator, males, 15 – Aktash, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3880083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880089>
    dc:description "Figs 17–20. Male genitalia of some Caryocolum species recorded from Altai Mts. 17 – C. mongolense Povolný, 1969, gen. prep. Bidzilya 192/18; 18 – C. procurvella sp. nov.; gen. prep. Šumpich 19979; 19 – C. atrum sp. nov., gen. prep. Huemer 1277; 20 – C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926), gen. prep. Šumpich 19985. Phalli to the same scale as genitalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3880089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880091>
    dc:description "Figs 21–22. Female genitalia of some Caryocolum species recorded from Altai Mts. 21 – C. atrum sp. nov., gen. prep. Huemer 1278; a – signum (enlarged); 22 – C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926), gen. prep. Šumpich 19984; a – detail of antrum (enlarged) (gen. prep. Bidzilya 286/17); b – signum (enlarged)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3880091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3880093>
    dc:description "Figs 24–28. Habitats of Caryocolum species in Altai Mts. 24 – Aktash, habitat of C. oculatella (Thomann, 1930) and C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926), the portable light trap in the middle of the photo; 25–26 – confluence of Argut and Karagem rivers, 25 km NW Dzhazator, habitat of C. arenariella (Benander, 1937), C. petryi (Hofmann, 1899), C. petrophilum (Preissecker, 1914), C. procurvella sp. nov., and C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926); 25 – view of the hill where Caryocolum species were collected; 26 – view of the landscape from the collecting site, in the background peaks of South Chuy ridge; 27 – Tara valley, 56 km SE of Dzhazator, habitat of C. arenariella (Benander, 1937), C. cassella (Walker, 1864), C. leucomelanella (Zeller, 1839), and C. tetrameris (Meyrick, 1926); 28 – Ukok plateau, habitat of C. atrum sp. nov. Photo J. Šumpich (24–27) and B. Wiesmair (28)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3880093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

